name: Brunch and Relaxing Out of The City
description: Let get out a bit of town and try to learn with a few different things with the real taste of Khmer food, the season of fresh fruit at very local and traditional market in the famous place for Cambodian people went there just for relaxing at the weekend., there was not just eating place for you, but there will give you more experience about Cambodian daily life with local area and people.
